\hline
Tasks & TvT & TvP & TvZ & PvP & PvZ & ZvZ \\
\hline
Baseline(\%) & 50.9 & 57.0 & 56.1 & 57.8 & 56.9 & 54.7 \\
\hline
Attention(\%) & 55.3 & 59.2 & 60.1 & 62.5 & 61.3 & 58.4 \\
